			<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading" lang="en"><i>The Life of Josiah Henson, Formerly a Slave, Now an Inhabitant of Canada, as Narrated by Himself</i></h1>
									<div id="bodyContent" class="mw-body-content">
